title: Khaby Lame net worth: Inside the $1 billion Rich Sparkle Holdings deal that raised billionaire rumors around TikTok star
summary_full: Khaby Lame’s nearly $1 billion deal is an all-stock agreement with Rich Sparkle Holdings, not a cash payout. The deal makes him a major shareholder and includes plans for an AI digital version of him. Despite online rumors, he has not retired and did not receive upfront cash.
